content.raw: Any additional operations being performed in there would skew the results of the performance test. I think we can just remove the assignment operation. I put it in there because sometimes compilers will erase lines if they can prove that the line won't have any "visible effect", but I don't believe the compiler will be allowed to do that in this case anyway.
